FEATURES OVERVIEW

👥 MASS ADDING
Add hundreds of members daily to your groups and channels. Support for both public and private groups, supergroups, and channels. Smart queue system prevents flooding.

🎯 TARGETED FILTERS
Add only real active users based on:
- Language preferences
- Last seen status
- Profile photo presence
- Account age
- Bio keywords
- Group activity level

🛡️ ANTI-BAN PROTECTION
Advanced protection system prevents Telegram limits and blocks:
- Auto delay between adds (customizable)
- Daily add limits (50-500 users)
- Proxy support (HTTP/SOCKS5)
- Multi-account rotation
- Cooldown management
- CAPTCHA auto-solver

📊 SOURCES
Extract members from multiple sources:
- Target groups (scrape members)
- Competitor channels
- Public group crawler
- CSV import (existing user lists)
- Phone book contacts

⚙️ AUTOMATION
Fully automated with smart features:
- Schedule adding (set time/date)
- Auto-scroll through member lists
- Skip already added users
- Duplicate removal
- Success rate tracking

📈 ANALYTICS
Track your growth in real-time:
- Added members counter
- Success/failed ratio
- Daily limits remaining
- Proxy status monitor
- Account health check

